                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d588">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Loomis</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Lee</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1904-11-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 15, 1904</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Loomis instructs Mr. Lee to confer with the President of Panama, and to
                    tender, under the provisions of the treaty, assistance from the Government of
                    the United States in suppression of the seditious and mutinous troops, if such
                    be desired by the Government of Panama.)</p>
            </div>
